Package examples.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecuteAction
    This advanced example shows how to execute a server context action by simulating operator input.
    GetServerVersion
    This simple example illustrates how to connect to server remotely using Server API and get version of the server.
    ManageDevices
    This example illustrates creation and management of device accounts, modification of device settings, execution of device operations and asynchronous receiving of device events.
    ManageUsers
    This example shows how to create/delete user accounts and manage their settings remotely using Server API.
